12.0pt 12.0pt 12.0pt 12.0pt'><span lang=3DEN-US style=3D'font-size:10.0pt;
color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>I won't bore you with all the theory
behind fretted instruments and such, so don't be afraid to read on. This is=
 an
